# Architecture & I/O

## 1. Pipeline Workflow
아래는 파이프라인의 전체 실행 흐름도입니다.

::: {id="mermaid-lightbox" style="cursor: zoom-in; border: 1px solid #e3e6f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; margin-bottom: 2rem;"}
{% if workflows and workflows|length > 0 %}
```{mermaid}
flowchart TD
    classDef default fill:#ffffff,stroke:#888,stroke-width:2px,color:#000,rx:5px,ry:5px;
    classDef proc fill:#e6e6e6,stroke:#999,stroke-width:1px,color:#000,rx:5px,ry:5px;
    
    linkStyle default stroke:#757575,stroke-width:2px;

{% for part_title, task_list in workflows.items() %}
{% set safe_title = part_title.split('.', 1) | last | trim | replace('&', 'and') %}
    subgraph part{{ loop.index }} ["{{ safe_title }}"]
        direction TB
{% for task_key in task_list %}
{% set t_title = tasks[task_key].title if tasks[task_key] is defined else task_key %}
{% set safe_t_title = t_title.split('.', 1) | last | trim | replace('"', '') %}
        {{ task_key }} ["{{ safe_t_title }} ({{ task_key }})"]
{% endfor %}
    end
{% endfor %}

{% for edge in flowchart %}
    {{ edge }}
{% endfor %}

{% for part_title, task_list in workflows.items() %}
{% for task_key in task_list %}
        class {{ task_key }} proc;
{% endfor %}
    style part{{ loop.index }} fill:none,stroke:#b0bec5,stroke-width:2px;
{% endfor %}
```
{% else %}
<div style="text-align:center; padding: 40px; color: #888;">
  <i>⚠️ Pipeline configuration data is missing.</i>
</div>
{% endif %}
:::

## 2. Repository Structure
파이프라인의 핵심 코드 및 테스트 환경 디렉토리 구조입니다.

<div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
<div class="card-header bg-light">
<strong>📁 Source Directory</strong> (<code>{{ source_dir }}</code>)
</div>
<div class="card-body" style="max-height: 350px; overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
<pre style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.85em; background: transparent; border: none;"><code>{{ source_tree }}</code></pre>
</div>
</div>

{% if test_tree %}
<div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
<div class="card-header bg-light">
<strong>🧪 Test Directory</strong> (<code>{{ test_dir }}</code>)
</div>
<div class="card-body" style="max-height: 350px; overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: auto; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
<pre style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.85em; background: transparent; border: none;"><code>{{ test_tree }}</code></pre>
</div>
</div>
{% endif %}